3.5 Ingester Ring Quorum
Ingesters use a consistent hash ring with replication factor (default RF=3). You need:
minReplicas >= RF + 1
So with RF=3, minimum 4 ingester pods to survive a node failure while maintaining quorum. For
RF=1 (acceptable in dev only), 2 replicas suffice.
3.6 Java Agent Version Compatibility
Pyroscope Server 1.7.x 1.6.x Java Agent 0.14.x 0.13.x async-profiler 3.0 2.9 JDK Support
JDK 11, 17, 21
JDK 11, 17
Vert.x 4.x requires JDK 11+. Vert.x 5.x (virtual thread preview) requires JDK 21. Ensure agent
matches.
