PYROSCOPE_SERVER_ADDRESS http://localhost:4040 Distributor HTTP endpoint
PYROSCOPE_AUTH_TOKEN— Bearer token if auth enabled
PYROSCOPE_PROFILER_EVENT cpu Use wall for Vert.x reactive
PYROSCOPE_PROFILER_ALLOC 512k Allocation profiling interval
PYROSCOPE_PROFILER_LOCK 10ms Lock contention threshold
