GF --> ROUTE_QUERY
ROUTE_QUERY --> QF
QF -- "fan-out gRPC" --> QR
QR -- "in-flight" --> ING
QR -- "historical" --> SG
SG -- "index+blocks" --> S3
DIST -. "gossip :7946" .-> ML
ING -. "gossip :7946" .-> ML
QR -. "gossip :7946" .-> ML
SG -. "gossip :7946" .-> ML
style ObsNS fill:#e8f4fd,stroke:#2196F3
style Storage fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#4CAF50
style AppNS fill:#fff8e1,stroke:#FF9800
6.3 Write Path Detail (Vert.x → Object Store)
sequenceDiagram
participant JA as Java Agent<br/>(Vert.x Pod)
participant DIST as Distributor
participant ING1 as Ingester-0
participant ING2 as Ingester-1
participant ING3 as Ingester-2
participant S3 as Object Store
JA->>DIST: POST /ingest (pprof, wall-clock)<br/>every 15s, ~8KB payload
DIST->>DIST: Compute consistent hash ring<br/>select RF=3 ingesters
DIST->>ING1: gRPC Push(profile)
DIST->>ING2: gRPC Push(profile)
DIST->>ING3: gRPC Push(profile)
ING1-->>DIST: ACK
ING2-->>DIST: ACK
ING3-->>DIST: ACK
DIST-->>JA: 204 No Content
Note over ING1,ING3: Buffering in-memory WAL<br/>Flush every 2h (min_block_duration)
ING1->>S3: Upload Parquet block<br/>+ index (TSDB)
ING2->>S3: Upload Parquet block
ING3->>S3: Upload Parquet block
S3-->>ING1: 200 OK
6.4 Read Path Detail (Grafana Query)
sequenceDiagram
participant GF as Grafana
participant QF as Query Frontend
participant QR1 as Querier-1
participant QR2 as Querier-2
participant ING as Ingester
participant SG as Store Gateway
participant S3 as Object Store
GF->>QF: HTTP GET /pyroscope/render<br/>?query=process_cpu:cpu:nanoseconds:cpu:nanoseconds<br/>&f
QF->>QF: Split query into sub-ranges<br/>Fan out to queriers
par Recent data (in-flight)
QF->>QR1: gRPC QueryRange(last 2h)
QR1->>ING: gRPC Query(WAL)
ING-->>QR1: Profile samples
QR1-->>QF: Partial result
and Historical data
QF->>QR2: gRPC QueryRange(older)
QR2->>SG: gRPC Query(blocks)
SG->>S3: Fetch block index + postings
S3-->>SG: Block data
SG-->>QR2: Profile samples
QR2-->>QF: Partial result
end
QF->>QF: Merge + deduplicate results
QF-->>GF: Flame graph JSON
