Deploy ingesters (StatefulSet) Deploy distributors Deploy query path (QF, Querier, SG) Deploy compactor Smoke test + ring validation :d1, after i3, 2d
:d2, after d1, 1d
:d3, after d2, 1d
:d4, after d3, 1d
:d5, after d4, 1d
